PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with the Provinces of Alberta, B.C., Manitoba, N.B., N.S., Ontario, P.E.I., Quebec and Saskatchewan, which will permit a province to opt out of the NATIONAL TRIPARTITE PRICE STABILIZATION PLAN FOR HONEY as early as the end of the 1992 crop-year, i.e. May 31, 1993 (Amendment No. 2).

Authority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT with the Provinces of
Alberta, B.C., Manitoba, N.B., N.S., Ontario, P.E.I., Quebec and
Saskatchewan, which will permit a province to opt out of the NATIONAL
TRIPARTITE PRICE STABILIZATION PLAN FOR HONEY as early as the end of the
1992 crop-year, i.e. May 31, 1993 (Amendment No. 2).
